{"word":"πηγάζω","slug":"πηγάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πηγάζω</b></el> <el>(πηγάζω,) ( φυτ. <el>-άσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πηγή'><el>πηγή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to spring</i> or <i>gush forth</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn. <i>to gush forth with</i> water, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}